# Project Goal
Create a Raspberry Pi 5-based wildlife camera system that automatically detects and identifies animals.
The system will detect motion. If something is detected, it will take a photo and send it to Telegram.

# Technical Requirements
- Hardware: Raspberry Pi 5 with connected camera module
- Primary Language: Python

# Structure
- /src contains the source code
- /data contains the data
- /docs contains the documentation
- /test contains the test code

# Tools:
For any console edits, use VIM instead of nano.
